 es (LG)\n3. ☑ +Convert Word form to fillable PDF+ Make Word memo\n   • ☑ n
 eed to install Adobe Acrobat Pro\n   • ☑ better just make a simple Word do
 cument and *avoid form\n     fields altogether*\n4. Handle special cases\n
 5. ☒ Tasks on forms [3/4]\n   1. ☑ Fill out forms (LG)\n   2. ☑ Create Doc
 usign (LG)\n   3. ☑ Sign Docusign (HB\, RK\, advisors)\n   4. ☒ Email comp
 leted forms (HB)\n      1. *include Lisa\, GPD\, +(advisors?)+ on email to
  students*\n      2. download final PDF from Docusign (apps.docusign.com)\
 n      3. use previous email as a template\n         • *for 3rd semester\,
  include text in email regarding\n            future milestones and timing
 *\n      4. proceed in alphabetical/chronological order
